name: Suspicious Crispy Roast
desc: Large chunks of roasted meat. Swiftly snatched from the choking black smoke, the roasted meat looks more like charcoal. Before the embers in the grill have faded, it's worth trying to make another batch.

value.text: Increases all party members' ATK by 160 for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
